text: Jamal Woolard (born July 8, 1975) is an American stand-up comedian, actor, rapper, and comedian. He is best known for portraying The Notorious B.I.G. in Notorious. ==Awards and nominations== * BET Awards ** 2009: Best Actor, Nominated * Black Reel Awards ** 2010: Best Breakthrough Performance (Notorious), Nominated ** 2010: Best Ensemble (Notorious), Nominated ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Comedians from New York City Category:American movie actors Category:Rappers from New York (state) Category:Actors from New York City Category:Singers from New York City Category:Living people Category:1975 births
